In Africa our believe is that no king actually died, but disappears in to the wind and one day, a lady have a dream that she saw the past king in the wind and the king sent this lady to the of the palace and when she delivered the message, the present king ignore the message, then the lady slept again one day and saw the said king again and the king again sent hey to the present king, the lady then again went to deliver the message and as usual the present king ignore the picture and the past king now ask the lady if she can do the job for him and the lady accepted and carried on the job, the the past king make her a wealthy lady in all their environ and when people asked her how come the too much wealthy, she do told them it's from wind King.
